  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't know whether the name Herb Brin means anything to you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Herb Brin publishes which is an Anglo-Jewish newspaper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was my tipster down at the If something came up at the wire that came his way, he'd say, hey such and such is having-- better get-- get going.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, any-- anything that would have a Jewish angle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like let us assume-- let us assume there was two alleged rabbis who are now in trouble.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This would have happened at-- while-- while Brin was on there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, look, two rabbis are-- can you do something?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then I would figure out, what do we do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do I get the board of rabbis to go and ban them, you know, like they did in the olden days?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, at least he would tip me off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can I do something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'd get the board of rabbis to issue a statement or what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, it depends on what I find out and what is there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's-- my mother used to say, I'm going into the [GERMAN]-- this is where you can kept your food-- to see what we're going to eat tonight.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What do you think, possibly, is the most important-- of all the-- of all the things that you did at that time-- what do you think is the most important to talk about?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think it's-- it's in two different ways.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, as I've said before, is the News Research Service, because my feeling was, because having been in newspapers, make the world know in this bound volume-- in this bound volume of that one newspaper that we published in Chicago-- the dedication, say something-- to awaken the public, you know.",
      "word_count": 50
    }
  ],
